Package hu.bme.mit.theta.cfa.dsl.gen

Class CfaDslBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.cfa.dsl.gen.CfaDslBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CfaDslListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class CfaDslBaseListener extends Object implements CfaDslListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CfaDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
